<p>Listings with complete information get <a href="https://www.webfx.com/blog/seo/google-business-profile-benchmarks/">7x more clicks</a> than incomplete ones. Fill in services, business description (750 characters), hours, attributes, and your service area. Add 15 or more photos and upload new images monthly.</p>
<h3>Post Regularly</h3>
<p>Post 2 to 3 times per week. Share recent wedding highlights, seasonal availability, and behind-the-scenes content. <a href="/blog/gbp-posting-frequency/">GBP posts</a> signal freshness to Google. Active listings rank higher than dormant ones.</p>
